snippet.title: R3 Review for the Commodore Amiga by John Gage
snippet.description: R3 is a gravity shoot 'em up / collect 'em up game for 1 or 2 players. Good game with a bit of humor. This was a game request by Amiga Bang. Warning! This video has swearing.
